Summary: took two picture less then 2 sec apart one picture had a ufo in it
divs: Sighting Detailsstopped on the side of the road to take a picture of a barn and some corn took 2 pictures came back to the house to unload onto the computer and saw it, The night before i also, around 9:30 10:00 p.m. i saw one in the western sky it look like a backwards meteor it was bright and fade out quick going up into the sky.
